      "text": "Wait, looking at the execute_kw format more carefully:\n\nThe format for `execute_kw` is:\n```\nmodels.execute_kw(db, uid, password, model, method, args, kwargs)\n```\n\nWhere `args` is a list of positional arguments and `kwargs` is a dict of keyword arguments.\n\nFor `read`, the method signature is `read(ids, fields)` where both are positional.\n\nSo it should be:\n```python\nexecute(\"ir.ui.view\", \"read\", [[1117], [\"name\", \"arch_db\", \"active\"]])\n```\n\nAnd for `write`, it should be:\n```python\nexecute(\"ir.ui.view\", \"write\", [[1117], {\"active\": False}])\n```\n\nLet me also fix the write calls.",
