ng a no-op to force recompile\n48: # Find all qweb views referencing appointment\n49: qweb_views = execute(\"ir.qweb\", \"search\", [[[\"ir.ui.view\", \"name\", \"ilike\", \"appointment\"]]])\n50: print(f\"Found {len(qweb_views)} qweb views matching 'appointment'\")\n51: \n52: print(\"\\nDone! The H1/title should now show 'Discovery Consultation'\")\n53: print(\"If not, wait ~1h for full cache TTL expiry or clear from Website editor.\")\n\n(End of file - total 53 lines)\n</content>",
