      "text": "Everything in the DB is correct:\n- **Appointment type**: name='Discovery Consultation', published=True, staff=[2] ✅\n- **Invite 27e80afd**: staff_user_ids=[2], appointment_type_ids=[1] ✅\n\nThe data is perfect. The only issue is QWeb cache. Let me aggressively bust it by editing the arch and touching all related views:",
