y/functions \"This path skips through empty directories\")\n\n[screenshots](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/tree/master/screenshots \"screenshots\")\n\n[screenshots](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/tree/master/screenshots \"screenshots\")\n\n[uploads](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/tree/master/uploads \"uploads\")\n\n[uploads](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/tree/master/uploads \"uploads\")\n\n[.gitignore](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/.gitignore \".gitignore\")\n\n[.gitignore](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/.gitignore \".gitignore\")\n\n[404.html](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/404.html \"404.html\")\n\n[404.html](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/404.html \"404.html\")\n\n[DESIGN.md](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/DESIGN.md \"DESIGN.md\")\n\n[DESIGN.md](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/DESIGN.md \"DESIGN.md\")\n\n[README.md](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/README.md \"README.md\")\n\n[README.md](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/README.md \"README.md\")\n\n[\\_headers](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/_headers \"_headers\")\n\n[\\_headers](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/_headers \"_headers\")\n\n[\\_redirects](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/_redirects \"_redirects\")\n\n[\\_redirects](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/_redirects \"_redirects\")\n\n[admin.html](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/admin.html \"admin.html\")\n\n[admin.html](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/admin.html \"admin.html\")\n\n[index.html](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/index.html \"index.html\")\n\n[index.html](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/index.html \"index.html\")\n\n[netlify.toml](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/netlify.toml \"netlify.toml\")\n\n[netlify.toml](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/netlify.toml \"netlify.toml\")\n\n[package.json](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/package.json \"package.json\")\n\n[package.json](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/package.json \"package.json\")\n\n[support.js](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/support.js \"support.js\")\n\n[support.js](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/blob/master/support.js \"support.js\")\n\nView all files\n\n## Repository files navigation\n\n-   [README](#)\n\n# AKcloud — Coming Soon Site\n\n[](#akcloud--coming-soon-site)\n\nSovereign-cloud landing page for AKcloud / AndieKobbieTech. Static-first, with a small backend on Netlify for real lead capture and future Odoo integration.\n\n## Stack\n\n[](#stack)\n\n-   **Frontend**: Plain HTML + CSS + vanilla JS (no build step)\n-   **Hosting**: Netlify (static)\n-   **Forms**: Netlify Forms (`data-netlify=\"true\"`)\n-   **Functions**: Netlify Functions (serverless, Node 18+)\n-   **Email**: Resend (optional, via Function webhook)\n-   **Booking backend**: Odoo (eventually sovereign on OCI + Elestio)\n\n## Local dev\n\n[](#local-dev)\n\n# Install Netlify CLI for local Functions testing\nnpm install \\-g netlify\\-cli\n\n# Start local dev server (functions + site together)\nnetlify dev\n\nThen open [http://localhost:8888](http://localhost:8888)\n\n## Deploy\n\n[](#deploy)\n\n### Option A — Connect to GitHub (recommended for ongoing work)\n\n[](#option-a--connect-to-github-recommended-for-ongoing-work)\n\n1.  Push this folder to a new GitHub repo\n2.  Netlify dashboard → **Add new site → Import existing project** → pick the repo\n3.  Build settings: leave defaults (no build command, publish directory = `.`)\n4.  Click **Deploy site**\n\nEvery push redeploys automatically. PRs get preview URLs.\n\n### Option B — Drag-and-drop\n\n[](#option-b--drag-and-drop)\n\nDrag this folder onto [https://app.netlify.com/drop](https://app.netlify.com/drop). Live in 30 seconds.\n\n## Functions\n\n[](#functions)\n\nPath\n\nPurpose\n\nAuth\n\n`/.netlify/functions/health`\n\nHealth check + deploy info\n\nNone\n\n`/.netlify/functions/notify-signup`\n\nReceives form-submission webhooks; logs, emails, Slack\n\nNetlify-internal\n\n`/.netlify/functions/get-waitlist`\n\nReturns recent submissions as JSON for admin\n\nBasic auth\n\n`/.netlify/functions/submit-booking`\n\nProxies bookings to sovereign Odoo via XML-RPC\n\nNone (add later)\n\nThe `/api/*` path is rewired to `/.netlify/functions/*` in `netlify.toml`.\n\n## Environment variables\n\n[](#environment-variables)\n\nSet these in **Netlify dashboard → Site settings → Environment variables**:\n\nVariable\n\nRequired for\n\nNotes\n\n`RESEND_API_KEY`\n\nEmail notifications\n\nFrom resend.com\n\n`NOTIFY_EMAIL`\n\nEmail notifications\n\nWhere signup emails go\n\n`SLACK_WEBHOOK`\n\nSlack/Discord alerts\n\nOptional\n\n`ADMIN_USER`\n\n`/api/get-waitlist`\n\nPick a strong username\n\n`ADMIN_PASS`\n\n`/api/get-waitlist`\n\nPick a strong password\n\n`NETLIFY_SITE_ID`\n\n`/api/get-waitlist`\n\nFrom API access token\n\n`NETLIFY_API_TOKEN`\n\n`/api/get-waitlist`\n\nPersonal access token from Netlify\n\n`ODOO_URL`\n\n`/api/submit-booking`\n\n[https://your-sovereign-odoo.example.com](https://your-sovereign-odoo.example.com)\n\n`ODOO_DB`\n\n`/api/submit-booking`\n\nDB name\n\n`ODOO_USER`\n\n`/api/submit-booking`\n\nAPI user email\n\n`ODOO_API_KEY`\n\n`/api/submit-booking`\n\nFrom Odoo → User → API Keys\n\n## Security\n\n[](#security)\n\n-   All HTML has `X-Frame-Options: DENY`, `nosniff`, `HSTS`, `Referrer-Policy`\n-   `/admin.html` is `noindex, nofollow`\n-   Turn on **Visitor access password protection** in Netlify dashboard for `/admin`\n-   HSTS preload submitted — register at [https://hstspreload.org](https://hstspreload.org) once you're sure\n\n## Roadmap\n\n[](#roadmap)\n\n-    Static landing page deployed to Netlify\n-    Netlify Forms for the email signup\n-    Functions for notification + admin API + Odoo proxy\n-    Sovereign Odoo on OCI Always Free via Elestio (separate project)\n-    Switch `/api/submit-booking` from Odoo Online Free → sovereign OCI Odoo\n-    Replace localStorage waitlist with Netlify Forms API view in admin.html\n\nSee `odoo-sovereign-deploy-guide.md` in `Documents\\AKcloud\\` for the OCI + Elestio deployment walkthrough.\n\n## About\n\nNo description, website, or topics provided.\n\n### Resources\n\n[Readme](#readme-ov-file)\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n[Activity](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/activity)\n\n### Stars\n\n[**0** stars](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/stargazers)\n\n### Watchers\n\n[**0** watching](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/watchers)\n\n### Forks\n\n[**0** forks](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/forks)\n\n[Report repository](/contact/report-content?content_url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fandiekobbietks%2Fakcloud-site&report=andiekobbietks+%28user%29)\n\n## [Releases](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/releases)\n\nNo releases published\n\n## [Packages 0](/users/andiekobbietks/packages?repo_name=akcloud-site)\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n## [Contributors](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/graphs/contributors)\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n## Languages\n\n-   [HTML 61.4%](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/search?l=html)\n-   [JavaScript 38.6%](/andiekobbietks/akcloud-site/search?l=javascript)\n\n## Footer\n\n[](https://github.com)© 2026 GitHub, Inc.\n\n### Footer navigation\n\n-   [Terms](https://docs.github.com/site-policy/github-terms/github-terms-of-service)\n-   [Privacy](https://docs.github.com/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement)\n-   [Security](https://github.com/security)\n-   [Status](https://www.githubstatus.com/)\n-   [Community](https://github.community/)\n-   [Docs](https://docs.github.com/)\n-   [Contact](https://support.github.com?tags=dotcom-footer)\n-   Manage cookies\n-   Do not share my personal information\n\nYou can’t perform that action at this time.",
