      "text": "Now I understand the full picture. Let me read the admin.html to see if there are credentials stored there, and also look at the support.js and functions.\n\nThe user is asking:\n1. Do they need the Odoo Website app for the appointment page?\n2. They want the appointment page to match their AKcloud theme (dark, #39FF14 green, Exo 2/DM Sans fonts)\n3. They want me to find credentials to control the Netlify site\n\nLet me check admin.html and support.js for credentials.",
