      "type": "answer",
      "text": "Here's how:\n\n1. **Go to** `https://akcloud.netlify.app/admin.html`\n\n2. **Login** with:\n   - Email: `admin`\n   - Password: `admin`\n\n3. **Set the booking URL** — in the \"Consultation Booking Link\" section, paste:\n   ```\n   https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/book/27e80afd\n   ```\n   Click **Save & Apply**\n\n4. **Set Odoo connection** (optional, for the waitlist sync later):\n   - Odoo URL: `https://andiekobbie.odoo.com`\n   - Database: `andiekobbie`\n   - Username: `andiekobbietks@outlook.com`\n   - API Key: `4a4b79c4fa6716a3f294cb7279b24105218906d5`\n   - Click **Save Config** then **Test Connection**\n\nThat's it. Now when anyone clicks \"Book a Consultation\" on your landing page, it opens the Odoo booking page directly instead of the \"notify me\" modal.",
      "timestamp": 1782280844754
    },
