      "text": "Yes — easiest way:\n\n**Option 1: Gumroad (fastest)**\n- Upload PDFs to gumroad.com\n- They handle payments, delivery, VAT\n- Add a \"Cheat Sheets\" nav link to your site pointing to your Gumroad store\n- Zero code, live in 10 minutes\n\n**Option 2: Netlify + Stripe (your site)**\n- Create a `/cheatsheets` page with previews\n- Add Stripe checkout buttons\n- Netlify Function handles the payment webhook\n- More control, more work\n\n**Option 3: Netlify Forms + manual**\n- Add a \"Buy\" form on your site\n- People pay via bank transfer / PayPal\n- You email the PDF manually\n- Works for first 5 sales, doesn't scale\n\n**Start with Gumroad.** Add a nav link:\n```html\n<a href=\"https://YOURNAME.gumroad.com\" class=\"nav-link\">Cheat Sheets</a>\n```\n\nOnce you're making sales, migrate to your own Stripe integration. Don't build payment infrastructure before you have paying customers.",
