      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\index.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n528:         <p style=\"margin:16px 0 0; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#C8C8C8;\">A public sector pilot migrated off a costly hyperscaler contract onto a sovereign UK region, cutting annual cloud spend by roughly forty percent.</p>\n529:       </div>\n530:     </div>\n531:   </div>\n532: </section>\n533: \n534: <!-- FOOTER -->\n535: <footer style=\"position:relative; z-index:1; max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; box-sizing:border-box; padding:64px 40px 56px;\">\n536:   <div style=\"display:flex; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:40px;\">\n537:     <div style=\"flex:1; min-width:240px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; padding:18px 20px; background:#111; border:1px solid #242424; border-radius:8px;\">\n\n(Showing lines 528-537 of 1019. Use offset=538 to continue.)\n</content>",
