      "type": "answer",
      "text": "## Goal\n- Build AKcloud (sovereign cloud MSP landing site on Netlify + Odoo appointment booking system) and create educational cheat sheets as a product to sell to non-technical founders and engineers\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- User is Andrea Enning (AndieKobbieTech), NG18 UK, USW graduate\n- Hardware: Intel i5-7300HQ, 16GB RAM, GTX 1050 (2GB)\n- Short-term memory challenges with CLI commands — needs cheat sheet reference\n- Git author must be \"andiekobbie\" not \"opprah-maker\"\n- Don't push to GitHub until user is ready (Netlify credits exhausted)\n- Site theme: dark (#080808), neon green (#39FF14), Exo 2 / DM Sans / JetBrains Mono fonts, \"phosphorescent circuit board\" aesthetic\n- User prefers being walked through commands rather than having everything done for them\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- **Odoo backend fix**: disabled `tour_enabled` for user #2 to stop TourService crash\n- **Appointment type id=1**: name='Discovery Consultation', published=True, staff_user_ids=[2], message_intro with pills set, message_confirmation set, auto_confirm/is_always_confirm on\n- **Invite id=2** (short_code `27e80afd`): staff_user_ids=[2], appointment_type_ids=[1]\n- **QWeb cache bust**: archived/unarchived views 1117, 3328, 1118; modified view 1117 arch (space then clean) to force recompilation\n- **XML-RPC auth**: authenticated as `andiekobbietks@outlook.com` with API key, uid=2\n- **Both URLs verified 200**: `/book/27e80afd` and `/appointment/discovery-consultation-1`\n- **Splash animation redesigned**: AK zoom-in → Cloud slides from left → \"presents\" typewriter → \"powered by ANDIEKOBBIETECH.\" with logo\n- **Mobile fix**: `@media (max-width: 600px)` reduces font to `clamp(64px, 18vmin, 120px)`, adds `overflow: hidden` + `max-width: 95vw` to `#spx-presents`\n- **Typewriter width fix**: `spxType` keyframe width changed from `8.2em` to `12em` for correct \"presents\" display with 0.55em letter-spacing\n- **Educational Material section**: added 6 cards (n8n, Odoo, Docker, Python, Git, Cloud) + nav link to `index.html`\n- **Git author config**: set `user.name=andiekobbie`, `user.email=andiekobbietks@outlook.com`\n- **Cheat sheet created**: `AKcloud/Cheat Sheet.md` with commands for deploy, git, admin panel, Odoo API\n- **Netlify CLI installed**: `netlify login` successful, directory linked to `akcloud` project\n- **Netlify deploy blocked**: `JSONHTTPError: Forbidden` — credits exhausted, needs billing upgrade\n\n### In Progress\n- Pushing Educational Material section to GitHub (committed locally, not pushed — waiting for Netlify credits)\n- Creating sellable cheat sheet products (n8n, Odoo, Docker, Python, Git, Cloud tracks)\n\n### Blocked\n- **Netlify credits exhausted**: \"andiekobbietks's team has run out of credits\" — deploys disabled, site may go offline\n- **User needs to upgrade billing**: https://app.netlify.com/teams/andiekobbietks/settings/billing — add card to free tier (no charges unless overages hit)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Standalone appointment module**: No need for Odoo Website app — appointment pages work without it\n- **Gumroad for cheat sheets first**: Sell digital PDFs via Gumroad before building own Stripe integration\n- **Non-technical founder angle**: Gap in market — existing n8n/DevOps cheat sheets are developer-focused; founder-focused \"automate without code\" angle is untapped\n- **Two revenue streams**: AKcloud consulting (services) + cheat sheets (digital products), same audience\n- **Netlify CLI over GitHub deploys**: Bypasses CI pipeline, deploys directly from local machine\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Upgrade Netlify billing (add card to free tier)\n2. Run `netlify deploy --prod --dir=.` to push Educational Material section\n3. Verify splash animation renders correctly (AK → Cloud → presents → powered-by)\n4. Verify \"presents\" typewriter displays in full on both desktop and mobile\n5. Fix remaining \"Discovery Consultation & More\" → \"Discovery Consultation\" H1 (may need Website → Clear Cache from editor)\n6. Set up Gumroad account and create first cheat sheet PDFs\n7. Amend existing git commits to use \"andiekobbie\" author (optional, force-push needed)\n8. Add more cheat sheet cards as content is created (AI/ML, SQL, etc.)\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Odoo credentials**: URL=`https://andiekobbie.odoo.com`, DB=`andiekobbie`, User=`andiekobbietks@outlook.com`, API key=`4a4b79c4fa6716a3f294cb7279b24105218906d5` (should be rotated)\n- **Netlify admin**: `https://akcloud.netlify.app/admin.html`, login `admin`/`admin`, Odoo config stored in localStorage\n- **Logo files mislabeled**: `ak-logo.png` (1020x612) is actual hi-res; `@2x` is 510x306 (smaller!); `@4x` is 1020x612 (same as 1x)\n- **Splash timing**: AK in 0.3s, Cloud 1.6s, presents typewriter 3.0s, powered-by 5.0s, exit 7.0s, removed 8.0s\n- **Git safe directory**: `git config --global --add safe.directory C:/Users/LLM-Test/Documents/AKcloud/akcloud-deploy`\n- **Netlify project linked**: directory already linked to `akcloud` project via `netlify link`\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\index.html`: Main landing page — splash animation, Educational Material section, all CSS/JS\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\admin.html`: Admin panel — Odoo config, booking URL, waitlist\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\netlify.toml`: Build config, redirects, security headers, environment vars\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\DESIGN.md`: Design system — colors, typography, spacing, circuit patterns\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\support.js`: Auto-generated React runtime (do not edit)\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\assets\\`: Logo files (ak-logo.png, ak-mark2.png + @2x/@4x variants)\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\cheat-sheet.md`: Quick reference commands for deploy, git, admin, Odoo\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\opencode.md`: Session summary — career goals, constraints, progress history\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\fix_odoo_cache.py`: Temporary script (deleted) — XML-RPC cache busting",
