      "text": "Skip to content\nandiekobbietks\nakcloud-site\nRepository navigation\nCode\nIssues\nPull requests\nAgents\nActions\nProjects\nWiki\nSecurity and quality\nInsights\nSettings\nOwner avatar\nakcloud-site\nPublic\nandiekobbietks/akcloud-site\nGo to file\nt\nT\nName\t\t\nandiekobbietks\nandiekobbietks\nFix presents typewriter width and container overflow\n8d633a2\n · \n1 hour ago\nassets\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nattached_assets\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nnetlify/functions\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nscreenshots\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nuploads\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\n.gitignore\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\n404.html\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nDESIGN.md\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nREADME.md\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\n_headers\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\n_redirects\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nadmin.html\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nindex.html\nFix presents typewriter width and container overflow\n1 hour ago\nnetlify.toml\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\npackage.json\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nsupport.js\nInitial AKcloud deploy with Netlify Forms + Functions\n11 hours ago\nRepository files navigation\nREADME\nAKcloud — Coming Soon Site\nSovereign-cloud landing page for AKcloud / AndieKobbieTech. Static-first, with a small backend on Netlify for real lead capture and future Odoo integration.\n\nStack\nFrontend: Plain HTML + CSS + vanilla JS (no build step)\nHosting: Netlify (static)\nForms: Netlify Forms (data-netlify=\"true\")\nFunctions: Netlify Functions (serverless, Node 18+)\nEmail: Resend (optional, via Function webhook)\nBooking backend: Odoo (eventually sovereign on OCI + Elestio)\nLocal dev\n# Install Netlify CLI for local Functions testing\nnpm install -g netlify-cli\n\n# Start local dev server (functions + site together)\nnetlify dev\nThen open http://localhost:8888\n\nDeploy\nOption A — Connect to GitHub (recommended for ongoing work)\nPush this folder to a new GitHub repo\nNetlify dashboard → Add new site → Import existing project → pick the repo\nBuild settings: leave defaults (no build command, publish directory = .)\nClick Deploy site\nEvery push redeploys automatically. PRs get preview URLs.\n\nOption B — Drag-and-drop\nDrag this folder onto https://app.netlify.com/drop. Live in 30 seconds.\n\nFunctions\nPath\tPurpose\tAuth\n/.netlify/functions/health\tHealth check + deploy info\tNone\n/.netlify/functions/notify-signup\tReceives form-submission webhooks; logs, emails, Slack\tNetlify-internal\n/.netlify/functions/get-waitlist\tReturns recent submissions as JSON for admin\tBasic auth\n/.netlify/functions/submit-booking\tProxies bookings to sovereign Odoo via XML-RPC\tNone (add later)\nThe /api/* path is rewired to /.netlify/functions/* in netlify.toml.\n\nEnvironment variables\nSet these in Netlify dashboard → Site settings → Environment variables:\n\nVariable\tRequired for\tNotes\nRESEND_API_KEY\tEmail notifications\tFrom resend.com\nNOTIFY_EMAIL\tEmail notifications\tWhere signup emails go\nSLACK_WEBHOOK\tSlack/Discord alerts\tOptional\nADMIN_USER\t/api/get-waitlist\tPick a strong username\nADMIN_PASS\t/api/get-waitlist\tPick a strong password\nNETLIFY_SITE_ID\t/api/get-waitlist\tFrom API access token\nNETLIFY_API_TOKEN\t/api/get-waitlist\tPersonal access token from Netlify\nODOO_URL\t/api/submit-booking\thttps://your-sovereign-odoo.example.com\nODOO_DB\t/api/submit-booking\tDB name\nODOO_USER\t/api/submit-booking\tAPI user email\nODOO_API_KEY\t/api/submit-booking\tFrom Odoo → User → API Keys\nSecurity\nAll HTML has X-Frame-Options: DENY, nosniff, HSTS, Referrer-Policy\n/admin.html is noindex, nofollow\nTurn on Visitor access password protection in Netlify dashboard for /admin\nHSTS preload submitted — register at https://hstspreload.org once you're sure\nRoadmap\n Static landing page deployed to Netlify\n Netlify Forms for the email signup\n Functions for notification + admin API + Odoo proxy\n Sovereign Odoo on OCI Always Free via Elestio (separate project)\n Switch /api/submit-booking from Odoo Online Free → sovereign OCI Odoo\n Replace localStorage waitlist with Netlify Forms API view in admin.html\nSee odoo-sovereign-deploy-guide.md in Documents\\AKcloud\\ for the OCI + Elestio deployment walkthrough.\n\nAbout\nNo description, website, or topics provided.\nResources\n Readme\n Activity\nStars\n 0 stars\nWatchers\n 0 watching\nForks\n 0 forks\nReleases\nNo releases published\nCreate a new release\nDeployments\n2\n github-pages now\nPackages\nNo packages published\nPublish your first package\nContributors\n2\n@andiekobbietks\nandiekobbietks Andie Kobbie\n@opprah-maker\nopprah-maker\nLanguages\nHTML\n61.4%\n \nJavaScript\n38.6%\nFooter\n© 2026 GitHub, Inc.\nFooter navigation\nTerms\nPrivacy\nSecurity\nStatus\nCommunity\nDocs\nContact\nManage cookies\nDo not share my personal information\n\n\ndoes this just tell a bad actour all his waays into my infra?",
