    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Let me compile the audit results. Here's what I found:\n\n**README claims vs actual implementation:**\n\n1. ✅ **Animated landing page with custom CSS animations** — index.html has full splash animation system with `@keyframes spxAKIn`, `spxCloudIn`, `spxType`, `spxCursor`, `spxPoweredIn`, `spxExit`, `spxRadialPulse`, plus circuit trace animations (`akTrace`, `akNode`, `akShimmer`, `akFade`)\n\n2. ✅ **Email waitlist via Netlify Forms** — index.html line 356 has `<form name=\"notify\" data-netlify=\"true\">` and line 576 has the visible form with `onsubmit=\"submitNotify(event)\"`\n\n3. ✅ **Serverless functions** — All 4 exist: `health.js`, `notify-signup.js`, `get-waitlist.js`, `submit-booking.js`\n\n4. ✅ **Appointment booking system with Odoo** — `submit-booking.js` has full XML-RPC integration with `findOrCreatePartner()` and `createAppointment()`\n\n5. ✅ **Admin panel** — `admin.html` exists with Odoo config, waitlist table, booking URL management\n\n6. ✅ **Security headers** — Both `netlify.toml` and `_headers` have HSTS, X-Frame-Options, nosniff, Referrer-Policy, Permissions-Policy, noindex for admin\n\n**Gaps found:**\n\n1. ⚠️ **admin.html waitlist is localStorage-only** — The admin panel reads from `localStorage('ak_notify_list')` instead of calling `get-waitlist` function. The README claims \"real-time admin dashboard\" but it's actually browser-local only. The `get-waitlist` function exists but admin.html doesn't use it.\n\n2. ⚠️ **No CSP headers** — README says \"Security hardened — HSTS, CSP headers\" but there's no Content-Security-Policy header in either `netlify.toml` or `_headers`.\n\n3. ⚠️ **index.html booking widget** — The booking widget uses `localStorage.getItem('ak_booking_url')` to get the booking URL, but the form on submit just shows a confirmation message without actually calling the `submit-booking` function. Let me check this more carefully.\n\nLet me read the booking section of index.html to verify.",
      "timestamp": 1782288455876
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "tool": "read",
      "code": "{\"filePath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\Documents\\\\AKcloud\\\\akcloud-deploy\\\\index.html\", \"offset\": 560, \"limit\": 230}",
      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\index.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n560:     <div class=\"tip-body\" id=\"tip-body\"></div>\n561:     <div class=\"tip-arrow\"></div>\n562:   </div>\n563: </div>\n564: \n565: <!-- BOOKING MODAL -->\n566: <div id=\"book-overlay\" onclick=\"closeBookingIfBackdrop(event)\">\n567:   <div class=\"book-modal\">\n568:     <button class=\"modal-close\" onclick=\"closeBooking()\">&times;</button>\n569:     <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:20px;\">\n570:       <img src=\"assets/ak-mark2.png\" srcset=\"assets/ak-mark2@2x.png 2x, assets/ak-mark2@4x.png 4x\" alt=\"AKCloud\" width=\"72\" height=\"36\" style=\"height:36px; width:auto; filter:drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(80,200,70,0.4)); image-rendering:-webkit-optimize-contrast;\">\n571:     </div>\n572:     <div style=\"font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#39FF14; text-shadow:0 0 6px #39FF14, 0 0 14px rgba(57,255,20,0.55); margin-bottom:12px;\">Book a Consultation</div>\n573:     <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 12px; font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:24px; color:#fff; line-height:1.2;\">Let's talk cloud.</h3>\n574:     <p id=\"book-sub\" style=\"margin:0 0 26px; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#787878;\">Our calendar opens at launch. Drop your email and we'll send you a booking link the moment we go live.</p>\n575:     <div id=\"book-form\">\n576:       <form name=\"notify\" method=\"POST\" data-netlify=\"true\" data-netlify-honeypot=\"bot-field\" onsubmit=\"return submitNotify(event)\">\n577:         <p style=\"position:absolute;left:-9999px;opacity:0;height:0;width:0;pointer-events:none;\"><label>Don't fill this: <input name=\"bot-field\" tabindex=\"-1\" autocomplete=\"off\"></label></p>\n578:         <label class=\"form-label\">Your email</label>\n579:         <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@company.com\" class=\"form-input\" id=\"book-email\" required>\n580:         <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"notify-me-launch\">\n581:         <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-sign-in\">Notify Me at Launch</button>\n582:       </form>\n583:     </div>\n584:     <div id=\"book-notify-msg\"></div>\n585:     <div style=\"margin-top:22px; padding-top:18px; border-top:1px solid #242424; text-align:center; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:#787878; letter-spacing:0.03em;\">powered by ANDIEKOBBIETECH<span style=\"color:#39FF14;\">.</span> &middot; consultations via Odoo</div>\n586:   </div>\n587: </div>\n588: \n589: <!-- LOGIN MODAL -->\n590: <div id=\"login-overlay\" onclick=\"closeLoginIfBackdrop(event)\">\n591:   <div class=\"login-modal\" id=\"login-modal\">\n592:     <button class=\"modal-close\" onclick=\"closeLogin()\">&times;</button>\n593:     <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:20px;\">\n594:       <img src=\"assets/ak-mark2.png\" srcset=\"assets/ak-mark2@2x.png 2x, assets/ak-mark2@4x.png 4x\" alt=\"AndieKobbieTech\" width=\"72\" height=\"36\" style=\"height:36px; width:auto; filter:drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(80,200,70,0.4)); image-rendering:-webkit-optimize-contrast;\">\n595:     </div>\n596:     <div style=\"font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#39FF14; text-shadow:0 0 6px #39FF14, 0 0 14px rgba(57,255,20,0.55); margin-bottom:12px;\">Client Portal</div>\n597:     <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 26px; font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; color:#fff;\">Sign in to <span style=\"color:#39FF14; text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(57,255,20,0.5);\">AK</span>Cloud</h3>\n598:     <label class=\"form-label\">Email</label>\n599:     <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@company.com\" class=\"form-input\" id=\"login-email\">\n600:     <label class=\"form-label\">Password</label>\n601:     <input type=\"password\" placeholder=\"••••••••\" class=\"form-input\" id=\"login-password\">\n602:     <button class=\"btn-sign-in\" onclick=\"signIn()\">Sign In</button>\n603:     <div id=\"auth-msg\"></div>\n604:     <div style=\"margin-top:22px; padding-top:18px; border-top:1px solid #242424; text-align:center; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:#787878; letter-spacing:0.03em;\">secured by ANDIEKOBBIETECH<span style=\"color:#39FF14;\">.</span> &middot; portal powered by Odoo</div>\n605:   </div>\n606: </div>\n607: \n608: <script>\n609:   // ── SPLASH ──\n610:   (function(){\n611:     var spx = document.getElementById('spx');\n612:     if (!spx) return;\n613:     document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';\n614:     // Start exit fade at 7.0s (powered-by fully visible by ~6.2s)\n615:     setTimeout(function(){\n616:       spx.style.animation = 'spxExit 1.0s ease forwards';\n617:     }, 7000);\n618:     // Remove from layout at 8.0s\n619:     setTimeout(function(){\n620:       spx.style.display = 'none';\n621:       document.body.style.overflow = '';\n622:     }, 6800);\n623:   })();\n624: \n625:   // ── COUNTDOWN ──\n626:   const LAUNCH_DAYS = 47;\n627:   const target = Date.now() + LAUNCH_DAYS * 24 * 3600 * 1000;\n628:   function pad(n) { return String(n).padStart(2, '0'); }\n629:   function tick() {\n630:     const s = Math.max(0, Math.floor((target - Date.now()) / 1000));\n631:     document.getElementById('cd-dd').textContent = pad(Math.floor(s / 86400));\n632:     document.getElementById('cd-hh').textContent = pad(Math.floor((s % 86400) / 3600));\n633:     document.getElementById('cd-mm').textContent = pad(Math.floor((s % 3600) / 60));\n634:     document.getElementById('cd-ss').textContent = pad(s % 60);\n635:   }\n636:   tick();\n637:   setInterval(tick, 1000);\n638: \n639:   // ── GLOSSARY ──\n640:   const GLOSSARY = {\n641:     msp: { t: \"MSP\", b: \"Managed Service Provider. A company that runs, secures and maintains your cloud and IT systems for you, so you do not need to hire an in-house infrastructure team.\" },\n642:     hyperscaler: { t: \"Hyperscaler\", b: \"The giant global cloud providers, Microsoft Azure, Amazon AWS and Google Cloud, that rent out computing power from enormous data centres.\" },\n643:     sovereign: { t: \"Sovereign cloud\", b: \"Your data and systems stay inside one country's borders and follow its laws. Here that means the UK, so nothing leaves UK jurisdiction.\" },\n644:     compute: { t: \"Compute\", b: \"Raw computing power: the processors and memory that actually run your apps, websites, databases and AI models.\" },\n645:     credits: { t: \"Cloud credits\", b: \"Free funding from the hyperscalers that you spend on their services instead of cash, often worth thousands to over a hundred thousand pounds for eligible startups.\" },\n646:     leverage: { t: \"Leverage\", b: \"To make full use of something you can already access, turning it into a real, measurable advantage.\" },\n647:     f6s: { t: \"F6S\", b: \"A global platform that connects startups with accelerators, grants, perks and investors. Pronounced eff-six-ess.\" },\n648:     production: { t: \"Production vs staging\", b: \"Production is the live system your real customers use. Staging is a private copy where changes are tested safely first, before they go live.\" },\n649:     architecture: { t: \"Architecture review\", b: \"An expert check of how your cloud system is designed, to catch security, cost and reliability problems before they cause damage.\" },\n650:     datastores: { t: \"Datastores\", b: \"Where an app keeps its information: the databases and storage that save and retrieve your records, files and data.\" },\n651:     byoc: { t: \"BYOC\", b: \"Bring Your Own Cloud. You keep your own cloud accounts and credits; we provide the architecture and management on top.\" },\n652:     byod: { t: \"BYOD\", b: \"Bring Your Own Device. Your team uses its own laptops and phones, secured and managed to company standards.\" },\n653:   };\n654: \n655:   const tipBox = document.getElementById('tip-box');\n656:   const tipTitle = document.getElementById('tip-title');\n657:   const tipBody = document.getElementById('tip-body');\n658:   let tipPinned = false;\n659:   let activeTerm = null;\n660: \n661:   // Detect touch-only devices — synthetic mouseenter/mouseleave must be ignored on these\n662:   const isTouch = () => window.matchMedia('(hover: none) and (pointer: coarse)').matches;\n663: \n664:   function showTip(key, rect) {\n665:     const g = GLOSSARY[key];\n666:     if (!g) return;\n667:     activeTerm = key;\n668:     tipTitle.textContent = g.t;\n669:     tipBody.textContent = g.b;\n670:     // position:fixed uses viewport coords — never add window.scrollY\n671:     const TIP_W = 272;\n672:     const GAP = 10;\n673:     let left = rect.left + rect.width / 2 - TIP_W / 2;\n674:     left = Math.max(GAP, Math.min(left, window.innerWidth - TIP_W - GAP));\n675:     tipBox.style.left = left + 'px';\n676:     if (rect.top > 80) {\n677:       tipBox.style.top = rect.top + 'px';\n678:       tipBox.style.transform = 'translateY(calc(-100% - 10px))';\n679:     } else {\n680:       tipBox.style.top = (rect.bottom + 8) + 'px';\n681:       tipBox.style.transform = 'none';\n682:     }\n683:     tipBox.classList.add('visible');\n684:   }\n685: \n686:   function hideTip() {\n687:     tipBox.classList.remove('visible');\n688:     activeTerm = null;\n689:     tipPinned = false;\n690:   }\n691: \n692:   document.querySelectorAll('.term').forEach(el => {\n693:     // Desktop hover — skip entirely on touch devices to avoid flicker\n694:     el.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {\n695:       if (!isTouch() && !tipPinned) showTip(el.dataset.term, el.getBoundingClientRect());\n696:     });\n697:     el.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {\n698:       if (!isTouch() && !tipPinned) hideTip();\n699:     });\n700:     // Click on desktop pins; tap on mobile shows and pins\n701:     el.addEventListener('click', e => {\n702:       e.stopPropagation();\n703:       const key = el.dataset.term;\n704:       if (tipPinned && activeTerm === key) {\n705:         hideTip();\n706:       } else {\n707:         tipPinned = true;\n708:         showTip(key, el.getBoundingClientRect());\n709:       }\n710:     });\n711:   });\n712: \n713:   // Click anywhere outside a term closes the tooltip\n714:   document.addEventListener('click', () => { if (tipPinned) hideTip(); });\n715: \n716:   // Scroll closes — passive for performance\n717:   window.addEventListener('scroll', () => { if (tipPinned) hideTip(); }, { passive: true });\n718: \n719:   // ── BOOKING ──\n720:   function openBooking() {\n721:     const url = localStorage.getItem('ak_booking_url');\n722:     if (url && url.trim()) {\n723:       window.open(url.trim(), '_blank', 'noopener,noreferrer');\n724:       return;\n725:     }\n726:     // Odoo not yet configured — show notify-me modal\n727:     const ov = document.getElementById('book-overlay');\n728:     ov.classList.add('visible');\n729:     document.getElementById('book-notify-msg').classList.remove('visible');\n730:     document.getElementById('book-notify-msg').textContent = '';\n731:     document.getElementById('book-email').value = '';\n732:     document.getElementById('book-form').style.display = 'block';\n733:     setTimeout(() => document.getElementById('book-email').focus(), 80);\n734:   }\n735:   function closeBooking() {\n736:     document.getElementById('book-overlay').classList.remove('visible');\n737:   }\n738:   function closeBookingIfBackdrop(e) {\n739:     if (e.target === document.getElementById('book-overlay')) closeBooking();\n740:   }\n741:   let notifyTimer;\n742:   async function submitNotify(event) {\n743:     event.preventDefault();\n744:     const form = event.target;\n745:     const email = document.getElementById('book-email').value.trim();\n746:     const msg = document.getElementById('book-notify-msg');\n747:     if (!email || !email.includes('@')) {\n748:       msg.textContent = 'please enter a valid email address.';\n749:       msg.style.color = '#ff5555';\n750:       msg.classList.add('visible');\n751:       return false;\n752:     }\n753:     // Always keep a local copy as a fallback\n754:     const list = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('ak_notify_list') || '[]');\n755:     if (!list.find(function(e){ return (e.email||e) === email; })) {\n756:       list.push({ email: email, ts: Date.now() });\n757:       localStorage.setItem('ak_notify_list', JSON.stringify(list));\n758:     }\n759:     // Submit to Netlify Forms via fetch (so the page doesn't reload)\n760:     try {\n761:       const body = new URLSearchParams(new FormData(form)).toString();\n762:       const res = await fetch('/', {\n763:         method: 'POST',\n764:         headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' },\n765:         body: body\n766:       });\n767:       if (!res.ok) throw new Error('Netlify rejected submission: ' + res.status);\n768:       document.getElementById('book-form').style.display = 'none';\n769:       msg.style.color = '#39FF14';\n770:       msg.textContent = '\\u2713 confirmed. we\\u2019ll reach out the moment booking opens.';\n771:       msg.classList.add('visible');\n772:     } catch (err) {\n773:       // Submission failed but the local copy is still saved\n774:       console.warn('[AKcloud] Netlify form submission failed; saved locally:', err);\n775:       document.getElementById('book-form').style.display = 'none';\n776:       msg.style.color = '#39FF14';\n777:       msg.textContent = '\\u2713 saved. we\\u2019ll reach out the moment booking opens.';\n778:       msg.classList.add('visible');\n779:     }\n780:     return false;\n781:   }\n782: \n783:   // ── LOGIN MODAL ──\n784:   function openLogin() {\n785:     document.getElementById('login-overlay').classList.add('visible');\n786:     document.getElementById('auth-msg').classList.remove('visible');\n787:     document.getElementById('auth-msg').textContent = '';\n788:     document.getElementById('login-email').value = '';\n789:     document.getElementById('login-password').value = '';\n\n(Showing lines 560-789 of 1018. Use offset=790 to continue.)\n</content>",
