      "text": "Here's the full audit:\n\n| README Claim | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| Animated landing page | ✅ Done | Full splash + circuit animations |\n| Netlify Forms waitlist | ✅ Done | Form submits via fetch, localStorage fallback |\n| Serverless functions | ✅ Done | All 4 functions exist and are complete |\n| Odoo XML-RPC booking | ⚠️ Partial | Function exists but booking widget doesn't use it |\n| Admin panel live waitlist | ⚠️ Partial | Reads localStorage only, doesn't call get-waitlist function |\n| CSP headers | ❌ Missing | README claims it but not implemented |\n| Security headers (HSTS, etc.) | ✅ Done | In both netlify.toml and _headers |\n\n**Three gaps to fix:**\n\n1. **No CSP headers** — README claims it but doesn't exist\n2. **Admin waitlist is localStorage-only** — get-waitlist function exists but admin.html never calls it\n3. **Booking widget bypasses serverless proxy** — opens Odoo directly instead of using submit-booking function\n\nWant me to fix all three?",
