      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AKcloud — Sovereign Cloud MSP Landing Site\n2: \n3: A production landing page for a managed cloud services business, built end-to-end from first principles. Static-first architecture with serverless backend, real lead capture, and integrated booking system.\n4: \n5: ## What I Built\n6: \n7: A complete client acquisition pipeline:\n8: \n9: - **Animated landing page** with custom CSS animations (phosphorescent circuit board aesthetic, no frameworks)\n10: - **Email waitlist** via Netlify Forms with real-time admin dashboard\n11: - **Serverless functions** for email notifications (Resend), webhook processing, and API proxying\n12: - **Appointment booking system** integrated with Odoo backend via XML-RPC\n13: - **Admin panel** with live waitlist data, booking management, and Odoo configuration\n14: - **Security hardened** — HSTS, CSP headers, noindex admin routes, environment-based secrets\n15: \n16: ## Technical Approach\n17: \n18: | Layer | Stack |\n19: |---|---|\n20: | Frontend | Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS — no build step, no frameworks |\n21: | Hosting | Netlify (static + serverless) |\n22: | Forms | Netlify Forms with webhook processing |\n23: | Backend | Netlify Functions (Node.js) |\n24: | Booking | Odoo XML-RPC integration |\n25: | Email | Resend API via serverless functions |\n26: | Auth | Environment variables, Basic auth, OAuth2 for Odoo |\n27: \n28: ## What This Demonstrates\n29: \n30: - **End-to-end ownership**: From first wireframe to deployed production site with real integrations\n31: - **No-code to code bridge**: Started with drag-and-drop, identified limits, built custom solution\n32: - **Problem-solving**: Client needed sovereign data control — built Odoo integration that keeps data in their infrastructure\n33: - **B2B delivery mindset**: Every decision optimized for client trust (security headers, transparent booking flow)\n34: - **Automation**: Email notifications, waitlist management, booking confirmation — all automated via serverless functions\n35: \n36: ## The Problem It Solves\n37: \n38: A sovereign cloud MSP needed a professional landing page that:\n39: 1. Captures leads without depending on third-party form services\n40: 2. Books discovery consultations directly into their Odoo CRM\n41: 3. Keeps client data sovereign (not trapped in SaaS platforms)\n42: 4. Works without JavaScript frameworks or build pipelines\n43: \n44: **Result**: Zero-dependency stack that deploys in 30 seconds, handles real bookings, and maintains full data sovereignty.\n45: \n46: ## Running Locally\n47: \n48: ```powershell\n49: npm install -g netlify-cli\n50: netlify dev\n51: # Opens at http://localhost:8888\n52: ```\n53: \n54: ## Architecture\n55: \n56: ```\n57: ┌─────────────────┐     ┌──────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n58: │   Landing Page  │────▶│  Netlify Forms   │────▶│  Email Notify   │\n59: │   (Static HTML) │     │  (Lead Capture)  │     │  (Resend API)   │\n60: └─────────────────┘     └──────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\n61:          │\n62:          ▼\n63: ┌─────────────────┐     ┌──────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n64: │  Booking Widget │────▶│ Serverless Func  │────▶│  Odoo Backend   │\n65: │  (Vanilla JS)   │     │  (XML-RPC Proxy) │     │  (CRM + Calendar)│\n66: └─────────────────┘     └──────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\n67: ```\n68: \n69: ## Skills Used\n70: \n71: `n8n` · `Make` · `Power Automate` · `XML-RPC` · `Serverless Architecture` · `API Integration` · `Vanilla JavaScript` · `CSS Animations` · `Security Hardening` · `DevOps` · `Client-Facing Delivery`\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: *Built by Andie Kobbie — AI Solutions Consultant / Automation Engineer*\n\n(End of file - total 75 lines)\n</content>",
