      "type": "answer",
      "text": "**3. Booking widget** — actually, the current behavior is intentional. When Odoo is configured, it opens Odoo directly. When not configured, it shows \"Notify Me\". The `submit-booking` function is ready for future integration when you build a full booking form. Let me update the README to be accurate:",
