    {
      "type": "action",
      "tool": "read",
      "code": "{\"filePath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\Documents\\\\AKcloud\\\\akcloud-deploy\\\\README.md\"}",
      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\AKcloud\\akcloud-deploy\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: <p align=\"center\">\n2:   <img src=\"assets/ak-mark2@2x.png\" alt=\"AKcloud Logo\" width=\"120\" style=\"background:#080808; padding:16px 24px; border-radius:12px; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(57,255,20,0.5));\">\n3: </p>\n4: \n5: <h1 align=\"center\">AKcloud</h1>\n6: \n7: <p align=\"center\">\n8:   <strong>Sovereign Cloud MSP — Landing Site & Client Acquisition Pipeline</strong><br>\n9:   <em>Built end-to-end: from first wireframe to deployed production with real integrations</em>\n10: </p>\n11: \n12: <p align=\"center\">\n13:   <a href=\"#what-i-built\">What I Built</a> •\n14:   <a href=\"#live-demo\">Live Demo</a> •\n15:   <a href=\"#screenshots\">Screenshots</a> •\n16:   <a href=\"#technical-approach\">Technical Approach</a> •\n17:   <a href=\"#architecture\">Architecture</a>\n18: </p>\n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ## What I Built\n23: \n24: A complete client acquisition pipeline for a sovereign cloud MSP — zero frameworks, zero build steps, full data sovereignty.\n25: \n26: | Feature | Implementation |\n27: |---|---|\n28: | **Animated Landing Page** | Custom CSS animations — phosphorescent circuit board aesthetic, AK zoom-in intro, typewriter effects |\n29: | **Interactive Glossary** | Hover/tap tooltips explaining cloud terminology (MSP, sovereign, hyperscaler, etc.) — accessibility-first |\n30: | **Email Waitlist** | Netlify Forms with webhook processing → Resend email notifications → Slack/Discord alerts |\n31: | **Appointment Booking** | Odoo XML-RPC serverless proxy ready — opens Odoo booking page when configured |\n32: | **Admin Panel** | Live waitlist data, Odoo configuration, booking management, CSV export |\n33: | **Security Hardened** | HSTS, CSP headers, noindex admin routes, environment-based secrets |\n34: \n35: ---\n36: \n37: ## Live Demo\n38: \n39: **🔗 [akcloud.netlify.app](https://akcloud.netlify.app)**\n40: \n41: ---\n42: \n43: ## Screenshots\n44: \n45: ### Landing Page — Hero View\n46: <p align=\"center\">\n47:   <img src=\"screenshots/hero.png\" alt=\"AKcloud Landing Page\" width=\"800\" style=\"border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #242424;\">\n48: </p>\n49: \n50: *Full landing page with nav, countdown timer, and \"Coming Soon\" badge. Pure HTML/CSS — no JavaScript frameworks.*\n51: \n52: ### Interactive Glossary Tooltips\n53: <p align=\"center\">\n54:   <img src=\"screenshots/tip.png\" alt=\"Glossary Tooltip Feature\" width=\"800\" style=\"border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #242424;\">\n55: </p>\n56: \n57: *Hover any underlined term to see a plain-English explanation. Built for non-technical founders evaluating cloud services. Accessibility: works on touch devices, respects `prefers-reduced-motion`.*\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ## The Problem It Solves\n62: \n63: A sovereign cloud MSP needed a professional landing page that:\n64: \n65: 1. **Captures leads** without depending on third-party form services\n66: 2. **Books discovery consultations** directly into their Odoo CRM\n67: 3. **Keeps client data sovereign** — not trapped in SaaS platforms\n68: 4. **Works without JavaScript frameworks** or build pipelines\n69: \n70: **Result:** Zero-dependency stack that deploys in 30 seconds, handles real bookings, and maintains full data sovereignty.\n71: \n72: ---\n73: \n74: ## Technical Approach\n75: \n76: | Layer | Stack |\n77: |---|---|\n78: | Frontend | Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS — no build step, no frameworks |\n79: | Hosting | Netlify (static + serverless) |\n80: | Forms | Netlify Forms with webhook processing |\n81: | Backend | Netlify Functions (Node.js) |\n82: | Booking | Odoo XML-RPC integration |\n83: | Email | Resend API via serverless functions |\n84: | Auth | Environment variables, Basic auth, OAuth2 for Odoo |\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ## Architecture\n89: \n90: ```\n91: ┌─────────────────┐     ┌──────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n92: │   Landing Page  │────▶│  Netlify Forms   │────▶│  Email Notify   │\n93: │   (Static HTML) │     │  (Lead Capture)  │     │  (Resend API)   │\n94: └─────────────────┘     └──────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\n95:          │\n96:          ▼\n97: ┌─────────────────┐     ┌──────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n98: │  Booking Widget │────▶│ Serverless Func  │────▶│  Odoo Backend   │\n99: │  (Vanilla JS)   │     │  (XML-RPC Proxy) │     │  (CRM + Calendar)│\n100: └─────────────────┘     └──────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\n101: ```\n102: \n103: ---\n104: \n105: ## What This Demonstrates\n106: \n107: - **End-to-end ownership**: From first wireframe to deployed production site with real integrations\n108: - **No-code to code bridge**: Started with drag-and-drop, identified limits, built custom solution\n109: - **Problem-solving**: Client needed sovereign data control — built Odoo integration that keeps data in their infrastructure\n110: - **B2B delivery mindset**: Every decision optimized for client trust (security headers, transparent booking flow)\n111: - **Automation**: Email notifications, waitlist management, booking confirmation — all automated via serverless functions\n112: \n113: ---\n114: \n115: ## Running Locally\n116: \n117: ```powershell\n118: npm install -g netlify-cli\n119: netlify dev\n120: # Opens at http://localhost:8888\n121: ```\n122: \n123: ---\n124: \n125: ## Skills Used\n126: \n127: `n8n` · `Make` · `Power Automate` · `XML-RPC` · `Serverless Architecture` · `API Integration` · `Vanilla JavaScript` · `CSS Animations` · `Security Hardening` · `DevOps` · `Client-Facing Delivery`\n128: \n129: ---\n130: \n131: <p align=\"center\">\n132:   <strong>Built by Andie Kobbie</strong><br>\n133:   <em>AI Solutions Consultant / Automation Engineer</em><br>\n134:   <a href=\"https://github.com/andiekobbietks\">GitHub</a>\n135: </p>\n\n(End of file - total 135 lines)\n</content>",
      "status": "success",
