      "code": "{\"command\": \"git add netlify/functions/get-config.js netlify/functions/save-config.js index.html admin.html; git commit -m \\\"Add serverless config functions for cross-device booking URL\\\"\", \"description\": \"Commit serverless config functions\", \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\Documents\\\\AKcloud\\\\akcloud-deploy\"}",
      "output": "warning: in the working copy of 'admin.html', LF will be replaced by CRLF the next time Git touches it\nwarning: in the working copy of 'netlify/functions/get-config.js', LF will be replaced by CRLF the next time Git touches it\nwarning: in the working copy of 'netlify/functions/save-config.js', LF will be replaced by CRLF the next time Git touches it\n[master ba774b6] Add serverless config functions for cross-device booking URL\n 4 files changed, 118 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 netlify/functions/get-config.js\n create mode 100644 netlify/functions/save-config.js\n",
