      "text": "Done. Two new functions created:\n\n| Function | What it does |\n|---|---|\n| `get-config.js` | Returns booking URL to all visitors (cached 5min) |\n| `save-config.js` | Admin saves URL globally via Netlify API |\n\n**How it works:**\n1. **Visitor** → fetches `/api/get-config` → gets booking URL → cached in localStorage\n2. **Admin** → enters URL → clicks Save → calls `/api/save-config` → updates Netlify env var\n3. **Next visitor** → gets the new URL from the function\n\n**To activate:**\n```\ngit push --force\n```\n\nThen in Netlify dashboard, set these env vars:\n- `ADMIN_USER` = your username\n- `ADMIN_PASS` = your password\n\nThe functions are ready — they'll work as soon as Netlify credits refresh and you deploy.",
